\begin_layout Standard
Prepare a white sauce in the following manner:- Take a piece of butter or
 margarine, the size of half an egg, put it in a stewpan with a level tablespoon
ful of flour and stir over a slow fire, or a low gas jet, until well blended;
 then add by degrees from 
\begin_inset Formula $\nicefrac{1}{2}$
