\begin_inset Formula $\nicefrac{1}{2}$
\end_inset

 teaspoonful of vinegar.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Place in the sauce 2 medium-sized carrots and one turnip cut into small
 cubes, a minced onion, 
\begin_inset Formula $\nicefrac{3}{4}$
\end_inset

 of a teacupful of haricot beans, and the same quantity of dried green peas
 previously soaked and partly cooked, and a few thinly-sliced kidney beans.
